data.description: Between Soldotna & Kenai, come see this 3 bed, 2.5 bath 3495sf home. Private, secluded lot features abundant wildlife, NEW circle driveway screened by thick woods. NEW Fenced yard! Remodeled Master Bathroom on the main level ensuite & 2 bedrooms downstairs. Kitchen has ceramic tiled floor, bay windows, custom hickory cabinets, stainless appliances & great natural lighting. Upstairs bonus roomcould be a 4th bedroom, sauna, office area, central vacuum, HUGE pantry & tons of storage. Enjoy the CREEK running through this property that is conveniently located between Soldotna & Kenai. The lower level has a wet bar, wood stove & is built for entertainment and large gatherings. A very large, beautiful deck made of exotic Tigerwood. The New circle graveled drive is large enough to accommodate an RV, boat or your ATVs and the two-car garage is over-sized with a 16 foot wide door. A new furnace and water heater was installed in 2018. Carpets will be professionally cleaned prior to closing.
